		<p>My Le Creuset pans have survived 450 ovens for no knead, but if you&#8217;re particularly worried about it, unscrew the handle and replace it with a stainless handle that Le Creuset makes (<a href="http://www.bedbathandbeyond.com/product.asp?order_num=-1&#038;SKU=14676899" rel="nofollow">http://www.bedbathandbeyond.com/product.asp?order_num=-1&#038;SKU=14676899</a>) or I suppose a metal drawer pull from a hardware store would work just as well.</p>

