		<p>I made this today.  I had come across this page a month or so ago and then saw the recipe made on a show called &#8220;French Food At Home,&#8221; and decided to tackle it.  It is wonderful.  Our 4 year old proclaimed it &#8220;Deee-lish-us!&#8221;  I will be making this for Easter communion at church.</p>

