		<p>Franco, I hope you didn&#8217;t throw it out!  It is very sticky.  It might be less sticky if you measure the flour by weight &#8211; Cook&#8217;s Illustrated/America&#8217;s Test Kitchen says 15 oz.  And using bread flour, I think, will result in a less sticky dough than using all purpose (I&#8217;ll find out tomorrow.)</p>

		<div class="reply">
				</div>
				</div>
